{
  "stem": "268.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they would put us in a tent, like a circus tent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They took us to [GERMAN], which means delousing, actually, what word literally means.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And from there, took us to showers, actual showers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then I remember, in-- in the shower, I almost lost my life, too, because I fainted again when the hot water and the steam hit me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I just-- I just fainted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And before I knew-- I don't know how much time expired, but I was told that I was on a stack of bodies already stacked up at the entrance of the showers.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They-- they just threw me on the stack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I was still alive, until this buddy-- my-- I told you, we had a buddy system-- told the capo, he says, he's alive.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He just fainted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He faints a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So-- so they picked me up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it was a-- God bless him, if the-- if the person is still alive, and if he isn't, the One Above should be kind to-- to-- to the person.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was a Czech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I later found out that the Czech underground was very, very strong in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he spoke Czech to me, and I answered in Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we're-- and I told him, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He brought me some of the coffee, [? something. ?] And he poured it into my throat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he gave me a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I-- I-- I devoured it quickly and somehow came to myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he saved my life again because of-- of the showers and everything, you know, just, you know, just the ground gave from under me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And Buchenwald was as-- a lot of death camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Again, in-- in regular times-- when I say regular times, in-- in the other camps, we would march to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
